		<dl>
			<dt ap-translate="INFO_USE.MARKET_CON01">KRW Market : </dt>
			<dd ap-translate="INFO_USE.MARKET_CON02">Cryptocurrencies tradable with Korean Won (KRW)</dd>
		</dl>
		<dl>
			<dt ap-translate="INFO_USE.MARKET_CON03">BTC Market : </dt>
			<dd ap-translate="INFO_USE.MARKET_CON04">
				Other cryptocurrencies tradable with Bitcoin(BTC)<br/>
				-       Trading price for cryptocurrency is determined with BTC standard and converted price for KRW is indicated for reference purposes<br/>
				(i.e BTC standard price times current price of BTC/KRW)
			</dd>
		</dl>
		<dl>
			<dt ap-translate="INFO_USE.MARKET_CON05">TUSD Market : </dt>
			<dd ap-translate="INFO_USE.MARKET_CON06">
				Other cryptocurrencies tradable with True USD(TUSD)<br/>
				-       Trading price for cryptocurrency is determined with TUSD standard and converted price for KRW is indicated for reference purposes<br/>
				(i.e TUSD standard price times current price of TUSD/KRW)
			</dd>
		</dl>
	</div>
